Chester , a 6-year-old Pit Bull mix , was found as a stray in 2010 and had been living in shelters on Long Island . 
  He was adopted by a family in Michigan after a picture of him was shared on social media . 
  Chester had been housed at the North Fork Animal Welfare League since 2010 . 
  The picture was shared more than 6,000 times and Chester was adopted on Friday . 
 